WEBVTT

00:00:00.452 --> 00:00:05.579
Do you think the world is going
to be a better place next year?

00:00:06.120 --> 00:00:07.823
In the next decade?

00:00:08.657 --> 00:00:11.420
Can we end hunger,

00:00:11.444 --> 00:00:13.975
achieve gender equality,

00:00:13.999 --> 00:00:16.121
halt climate change,

00:00:16.145 --> 00:00:18.708
all in the next 15 years?

00:00:19.764 --> 00:00:23.668
Well, according to the governments
of the world, yes we can.

00:00:24.343 --> 00:00:26.961
In the last few days,
the leaders of the world,

00:00:26.985 --> 00:00:29.461
meeting at the UN in New York,

00:00:29.485 --> 00:00:32.240
agreed a new set of Global Goals